com.bluegosling.concurrent

Interface CompletionStageFuture<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the future value
    All Superinterfaces:
    CompletionStage<T>, Future<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RunnableCompletionStageFuture<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InterruptibleCompletableFuture, ReadOnlyCompletableFuture, RunnableCompletableFuture, RunnableReadOnlyCompletableFuture

    public interface CompletionStageFuture<T>
extends CompletionStage<T>, Future<T>
    A Future that also provides the fluent API of CompletionStage. This extracts a useful interface from CompletableFuture.
